Class RequestHandlingConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  om.RequestHandlingConfiguration

public class RequestHandlingConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object

From the provided requestHandlers.xml configuration File this class interprets it and then holds reference to the settings within the composite configurationSettings collection so that these can be examined at runtime.

Author:
Trevor Hinson
